message: ""It doesn't have to be a big city," said Valerio. "I think that a community that sleeps on the subject on trafficking is a community in danger for someone to come and start doing trafficking work, especially in small cities."

data.description: Truth Pharm held a garden of hope Monday night at the United Presbyterian Church of Binghamton to talk about human trafficking.
data.title: Truth Pharm talks human trafficking awareness
